CatDescriptText: Cutline of related article published in Pittsburgh Courier, November 5, 1955, pg. 14B reads: "African Premier Visits City - The Hon. Nnamdi Azikiwe, Prime Minister of Eastern Nigeria, West Africa, was in city, the guest of The Courier, Thursday, to advance plans for the establishment of the University of Nigeria..."
TitMainTitle: Eastern Nigerian Prime Minister Nnamdi Azikiwe wearing light colored agbada, eyeglasses and dark cap, seated at table with three other men wearing suits, in interior with square patterned curtains and chalkboard
